text: William D. Wulff (born 1949) is an American chemist, currently at Michigan State University and an Elected Fellow of the American Association for the Advancement of Science. ==References== Category:Fellows of the American Association for the Advancement of Science Category:21st-century American chemists Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:University of Wisconsin-Eau Claire alumni Category:Iowa State University alumni
